# AWP register edits

- **Canonical source:** `*.yaml` under `.awp-workspace/` — never edit generated `*.md` table views in place.
- After changing any register YAML, run `make awp-render` from the repo root.
- Terminal statuses: move rows from active YAML to matching `archive/*.yaml`, then render.
- Schema and column rules: `.awp-workspace/meta/schemas/register-schema-versions.yaml`
- Before handoff: `make awp-docs-check`

Design specs live under `docs/` — set `spec_link` and `decision_links` to paths there.

Workflow contract: `.awp-workspace/AGENTS.md`
